Meebugs are unique 3D voxel characters, created by a custom generative algorithm, then registered on the Ethereum blockchain. The collection plays with the Meebits iconography and is a continuation of the Larva Lads universe.

name: Koala Riot
description:
Welcome to Koala Riot, an innovative and captivating collection of NFTs where the charm of simplicity meets the cutting-edge capabilities of artificial intelligence. This unique series of digital artworks captures the essence of minimalist design, brought to life by the creative power of AI, featuring the delightful and unexpected world of koalas in a riot of minimalist splendor.

About the Collection:

Koala Riot is a thoughtfully curated series that showcases the playful and whimsical nature of koalas through a minimalist lens. Each piece in this collection is the result of sophisticated AI algorithms, which distill the essence of these adorable creatures into clean, simple, yet profoundly expressive artworks. This collection is a celebration of how AI can transform basic elements into evocative visual narratives.

name: OneMarket
description:
The OneMarket project is a social trading platform and is designed to change international trade and logistics around the world. The project's standards will forever change the vision of international trade. The project will ensure maximum security of supply chains, trade and financial relations between participants, and will also ensure maximum transparency in relations between business and the state. In fact, OneMarket will become a “trend setter” in international trade. The project's full launch date is January 1, 2025. Each of the NFTs offered is super unique and entitles the buyer to become the full owner of the company's shares. Each numbered NFT is equal to 1% of the company's shares. The sale period will be limited and will never be offered for sale again as it is now.
CEO and creator of OneMarket Renat Kuntishev is an accredited UN/CEFACT expert and has been working on issues of simplifying e-commerce for more than 9 years.

name: Defiant Art
description:
Welcome to our private family collection of nonconformist art! For over 40 years, we have collected unique pieces with love and dedication, which are now presented as NFTs on the OpenSea platform. Each image displayed is a digital version of an original that belongs to our family, ensuring their authenticity and exclusivity.

What is Nonconformism?
Nonconformism in art is a direction that arose in response to official and generally accepted norms and canons. Non-conformist artists strive for freedom of expression, experiment with shapes, colors and techniques, and challenge traditions and stereotypes. Their work is often provocative, original and filled with deep meaning. Nonconformist art embodies the spirit of rebellion and the desire for innovation.

Uniqueness of Our Collection: 
All NFTs presented are created from original paintings that belong to our family. These works are not available in mass circulation and are unique.
The collection includes works by famous nonconformist artists who made significant contributions to the development of modern art.
Each piece in our collection has its own unique history and style, which makes it diverse and rich in meaning.

Investment Attractiveness: 
Nonconformist art only increases in value over the years, making it a profitable investment for collectors and investors.
Purchasing an NFT from our collection gives you the opportunity to own digital evidence of a unique piece of art that is second to none.
By purchasing our NFTs, you become part of a community of connoisseurs and custodians of unique cultural heritage, which highlights your sophistication and taste.

We invite you to explore our collection and discover a world of nonconformist art filled with freedom, experimentation and deep meaning. Support independent creativity and become the owner of unique digital works that carry history and the spirit of the time.

Join us at OpenSea and become part of the history of nonconformist art!
